  "text": "To implement the segmentation method of hadith text from Sahih al-Bukhari corpus, we developed a tool for this process. This tool is made to prepare the hadith text for the hadith encoding prototype with TEI (more details in [2] and [CITATION_1] ). The implementation is based on JAVA language and the API JDOM Library. Fig. 4 presents the general architecture of this program. This tool is developed to extract automatically each hadith text from Sahih al-Bukhari then segment each one to Isnad and Matn which goes as input to the hadith encoding process.",
